  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<Usuari>, java.util.Collection<Usuari>, java.util.List<Usuari>, java.util.RandomAccess
    public class ConjuntUsuaris
extends java.util.ArrayList<Usuari>
    This class describes a set of users as a extension of a users ArrayList. It keeps the elements ordered by the id of users, to achieve a better performance when asking for a user with a certain ID.
